 <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Screen Printing</h2>
 <p class="mb-4 text-lg text-gray-400">
 Multi-color screen printing on tees, hi-vis vests, hoodies, and workwear. Bold, opaque prints that survive job-site abuse, industrial laundry cycles, and Nevada sun. Plastisol for punch and water-based for soft-hand crew tees — we pick the ink system that fits the job, not the one that's easiest.
 </p>
 <p class="mb-6 text-base text-gray-400">
 PMS color matching on runs of 48+ pieces. Up to 8 ink colors per placement. Large-format back prints, left-chest, pocket, and sleeve hits all available. Specialty inks — metallic, glow-in-the-dark, puff, and high-density — for events, crew-pride orders, or brand activations.
 </p>
